name: MegaSeth Snake Edition
description: MegaSeth will be released in 2 hand painted colour-ways, 10 pieces of each colour, making a total of 20 pieces. There will be 2 chase versions 1 in each colour-way, MegaSeth comes blind-boxed in a presentation box, along with special MegaSeth Rock Memorabilia, Gig Ticket, Mini Print, Real Plectrums, and Badges.

name: Govra Print
description:
From the beautiful mind of Sergey Safonov we present to you the Govra, The Deity of the End. Haling from Gooma world, which is full of gods, spirits, ghosts and deities of all kinds. You can find her where something ends – at the end of the road, see her at the end of the day or you can meet her when something dies. Govra has a large number of cultist followers, who build altars and praise her, sacrificing sandglasses and rotten fruits. 

We have a limited number of Govra Giclée prints available from our store at £10 each. 12" x 12" hand embossed and numbered.

name: Disney / Star Wars Mini Print Set
description: Star Wars/Disney mash-up designs, in 2 brand new colour-ways. Mickey Trooper in pink, and Boba Duck in green. Sized at A5 and available in a twin pack. Printed on a thick 350gsm card stock, hand embossed and numbered. Limited to 25 sets, priced at just £5 per set.

name: Adventure Time Print
description:
Mimic’s superb Adventure Time design. Only 20 of these will be released. A3 in size, hand embossed and numbered, priced at just £15 each. 

I tried to get Mimic to leave us with a detailed hypotheses, but all he said was the following "Its been fun and i wrote a lil song: Deadventure time, C'mon, stab your friends,  We'll go to very twisted Lands , Now wake the dead,  And skin the Human,  The Screams 'll never end,  It's Deadventure Time!"

name: Heavy Metal Qee Book
description:
64 page book, dedicated to the Heavy Metal Qee custom toy show. A spread dedicated to each artists piece, with full colour pictures of their completed custom Qee, and information about both the artist and their creation. Full colour glossy stock, perfect bound, and shrink wrapped to reach you in mint condition. 

All proceeds from the Heavy Metal Qee Customs and Books go to The Garden House Hospice.
